title: Largest and Smallest Humidity Differnence During a Year
name: Largest and Smallest Humidity Differnence During a Year
description: This dataset illustrates the largest and smallest humidity differences, in cities with 50,000 or more people, in a year.  A value of -1 means that the data was not applicable.  Also included are the housing population, the percent of humidity difference, the ranking, the inverse ranking to be used for mapping only, and the city and state.Source:  City-DataURL:  http://www.city-data.com/top2/c483.htmlhttp://www.city-data.com/top2/c484.htmlDate Accessed: November 13, 2007
